    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I haven&#8217;t eaten many cold soups, but one that I&#8217;ve enjoyed is the spicy melon soup at Matt&#8217;s in the Market. It&#8217;s a daily special in the summer, and is a great prelude to a hot catfish sandwich (one of my favorite summer lunches). When I had lunch there recently the sandwich of the day was salmon BLT, so Matthew and I each had half of each&#8211;best fish sandwich ever! (The melon soup was great too.)</p>
    </div>

